{"tid":1252064,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【咸豐恩怨】重提被汪明荃刺傷！黃淑儀：佢冇問候過我","createTime":"2019-06-22T20:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T14:50:29.000Z","uid":24160,"like":28,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"84e67060040beed8259b69ad332bb5b83db1e6aa","tid":1252064,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T20:10:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190622/photo/bkn-20190622132435723-0622_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190622173614\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190622%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190622132435723-0622_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190622173614&h=95073a93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃淑儀（GiGi姐）受訪商台節目《1圈圈 星光背後》，重提早年被翻於1976年為無線拍攝劇集《書劍恩仇錄》時，飾演李沅芷的GiGi姐，跟演霍青桐的汪明荃（阿姐）、演鴛鴦刀駱冰李司棋曾爆出過爭戲爭排位傳聞，更有指當年阿姐刺傷GiGi姐後鬧不和。<br />\n<br />\nGiGi姐對該次受傷歷歷在目，親述當時情況，稱他們拍劇用的劍、刀均是真金屬，故很容好易斷。她說：「有一場戲我撩佢（阿姐），佢嬲就攞把劍一打過嚟，我一擋，把劍一斷就飛咗嚟呢度（指著眉心）。」GiGi姐謂當時由李家鼎抱上車送去醫院縫針，醫生很好人，幫她縫得很幼，共縫了4針，疤痕不明顯，只有皺眉時就見到有一條痕。GiGi姐說當時沒驚：「意外嚟㗎嘛，係真係冇事，總之唔好插到我隻眼，或者我盲咗，咁我就識驚；當時有啲血流落嚟咁樣。」<br />\n對於被炒跟阿姐有恩怨，GiGi姐連聲否認：「冇冇冇，絕對冇，大家都知係意外，不過，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當時阿姐連半個電話都冇打嚟問，『你點呀』，或者『唔好意思』，冇！反而近年見到佢，佢自己攞出嚟講，『哎吔，當時呀，我把劍插親佢，真係幾唔好意思』，都過咗幾十年仲講嚟做咩，真係冇話唔開心，因為係意外。</span></span></strong>」<br />\n<br />\n電台錄音 : <a href=\"https://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=OEN190622-14893-1324-M&amp;d=1561185519\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Fhk%2Findex.html%3Fi%3DOEN190622-14893-1324-M%26d%3D1561185519&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaItKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=66a40c38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=OEN190622-14893-1324-M&amp;d=1561185519</a><br />\n<br />\nSources:　<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190622/bkn-20190622132435723-0622_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190622%2Fbkn-20190622132435723-0622_00862_001.html&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaItKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=8de3b859\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190622/bkn-20190622132435723-0622_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1528677/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82-%E9%87%8D%E6%8F%90%E9%81%AD%E6%B1%AA%E6%98%8E%E8%8D%83%E5%88%BA%E5%82%B7%E7%88%86%E4%B8%8D%E5%92%8C-%E9%BB%83%E6%B7%91%E5%84%80-%E9%80%A3%E5%8D%8A%E5%80%8B%E9%9B%BB%E8%A9%B1%E9%83%BD%E5%86%87%E6%89%93%E5%9A%9F%E5%95%8F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1528677%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582-%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%258F%2590%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25B1%25AA%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%258D%2583%25E5%2588%25BA%25E5%2582%25B7%25E7%2588%2586%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2592%258C-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E6%25B7%2591%25E5%2584%2580-%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%2580%258B%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%2586%2587%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%259A%259F%25E5%2595%258F&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaItKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=5b8810d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1528677%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582-%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%258F%2590%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25B1%25AA%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%258D%2583%25E5%2588%25BA%25E5%2582%25B7%25E7%2588%2586%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2592%258C-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E6%25B7%2591%25E5%2584%2580-%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%2580%258B%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%2586%2587%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%259A%259F%25E5%2595%258F&h=541ded14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1528677/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82-%E9%87%8D%E6%8F%90%E9%81%AD%E6%B1%AA%E6%98%8E%E8%8D%83%E5%88%BA%E5%82%B7%E7%88%86%E4%B8%8D%E5%92%8C-%E9%BB%83%E6%B7%91%E5%84%80-%E9%80%A3%E5%8D%8A%E5%80%8B%E9%9B%BB%E8%A9%B1%E9%83%BD%E5%86%87%E6%89%93%E5%9A%9F%E5%95%8F</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190622/_2019062216535434454.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190622%2F_2019062216535434454.jpg&h=156ea513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃淑儀重申當年受傷純屬意外。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190622/photo/bkn-20190622132435723-0622_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190622173614\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190622%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190622132435723-0622_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190622173614&h=cd1993bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃淑儀接受梁泰來訪問。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190622/photo/bkn-20190622132435723-0622_00862_001_03b.jpg?20190622173614\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190622%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190622132435723-0622_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20190622173614&h=a0d8a339&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當年黃淑儀（左二）拍《書劍恩仇錄》時被汪明荃（右三）不慎刺傷流血！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190622/_2019062216535557007.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190622%2F_2019062216535557007.jpg&h=73d45da1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾位阿姐早前難得相聚。（ig圖片）"},{"pid":"f37f03e3f817ea28f7772e0a1a2e36cee7f7a691","tid":1252064,"uid":152123,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T20:13:33.000Z","msg":"趙雅芝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdcd39f1f6fc0f8a921599c339129036c9f3a866","tid":1252064,"uid":24160,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T20:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/23e747.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.